INSERT INTO `wp_rg_lead_detail_long` VALUES (18,'NEW to the market!   Reach grassroots conservative donors who have demonstrated their support of the Tea Party movement and Tea Party candidates.\r\n\r\nAs we move toward Election Day 2012, these passionate Americans will be more eager than ever to financially support candidates who they feel will take a stand for the nation and uphold the Tea Party’s principles and beliefs. \r\n\r\nThese patriotic Americans want to see Obamacare repealed, an end to government bailouts, a reduction in personal and business income taxes, a reduction in the size of government, and political leaders that govern within the boundaries of the Constitution.   \r\n\r\nWho should test this list?   Conservative Candidates, Conservative PACs, Conservative/Tea Party organizations, Republican national committees and state parties.'),(12,'The College Republican National Committee is the largest, oldest and most active Republican youth organization in the country today.  \r\n\r\nThe donors to CRNC supported the Revolution 2012 effort which recruited and mobilized students to get-out-the-vote, volunteer on campaigns as well as fund media projects targeted at the college voting population.  This file will be updating.'),(23,'Target these highly-responsive donors for your charitable, veteran or health or issue mailing today!\r\n\r\nChristine O’Donnell was a candidate for U.S. Senate from Delaware and has experience as a recognized political commentator, marketing consultant, speaker, and author.  The ChristinePAC mission is to empower Americans to become involved in the voting process and commit these voters to conservative values that strengthen our nation.  \r\n\r\nStudies of donor behavior show that the individuals on the O’Donnell Masterfile make solid prospects for charitable and non-profit appeals.    These donors have a variety of interests including humanitarianism, Christian missions, supporting our troops, and healthcare.\r\n\r\n**This file is available for charitable and telemarketing offers only.**'),(29,'We The People consists of a unique audience of responsive conservative Republican donors.    Built through advanced data modeling techniques, We The People offers fundraisers a more-focused universe of premium donors. \r\n\r\nThe Platinum Model segment is divided into two categories:  Candidate and Conservative.   \r\nCandidate Platinum is a must-test for:\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Conservative Republican candidates</li>\r\n<li>Conservative Republican PACs</li>\r\n<li>Voter Outreach </li></ul>\r\n\r\nConservative Platinum is a must-test for:\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Charitable appeals</li>\r\n<li>Religious groups</li>\r\n<li>Product, book and subscription offers</li></ul>\r\n'),(35,'Target high-income earners who have proven their commitment to conservative organizations and candidates through donations of $100+ or more.  \r\n\r\nThe majority of indivduals on this list make over $100,000.    They are staunch supporters of private enterprise and the free market, they oppose Obamacare, and they want a drastic reduction in government and government regulations.    \r\n\r\nThe unemployment rate remains high.  There has been a decline in the number of start-up companies.  The middle class has only become weaker under Obama.  But these folks are still willing to give.\r\n\r\nAnd with their generous donation, they are sending an important message – “Hit the Road Barack!”   \r\n\r\nWho should test this list?   Conservative Candidates, Conservative PACs, Conservative/Tea Party organizations, Republican national committees and state parties.'),(40,'Michele PAC is the official political action committee of Congresswoman Michele Bachmann.   The PAC was formed in the summer of 2010 to support conservative, freedom-loving candidates across the nation and hold them accountable once elected.  After her presidential run Congresswoman Bachmann remains a leading and influential voice within the tea party movement and national political scene.'),(46,'These conservative donors have helped fund grassroots efforts to defend Christians and their freedom of religion.  They have donated to several initiatives that help defend the right to pray publicly and the preservation of long-standing and honorable values.    These donors are pro-life, pro-family and anti- gay marriage.  They believe one of our best defenses is to help elect into office like-minded conservatives who can fight for their Christian values and individual liberty.  '),(52,'<p align=\"center\">A GREAT LIST FOR ALL PRO-LIFE MAILERS!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fifty-five thousand strong!   This donor file consists of staunch pro-life Americans who have made direct mail contributions to a pro-life organization within the last 12 months.  </p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>POLITICALLY</em>:      Pro-Life America donors put their money behind pro-life candidates, pro-life public advocacy and legislation ending taxpayer- funded abortion.   They want to repeal Obamacare and defund Planned Parenthood.    Through support of tireless litigation efforts, they hope one day to see an overturn of Roe v. Wade.   These active donors also want President Obama and his abortion-on-demand policies out of office in 2012.  </p>  \r\n\r\n<p><em>SOCIALLY</em>:           Pro-Life America donors are pro-family and pro-traditional marriage.   Their Christian faith calls them to serve and give back making these donors excellent prospects for charitable/humanitarian appeals.   </p>\r\n'),(57,'<p align=\"center\"><strong>\"Behind the Man is the Movement\"</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now available to you: a <strong>rare and unique list of donors</strong> that believe Ron Paul’s principles are the only way to restore America. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>By far, <strong>the best</strong> source of liberty movement donors available…</em></p>\r\n \r\n<p>These passionate Americans believe strongly -- as our founding fathers did -- in the rights of the individual and limited government above all else.  They stress the importance of personal accountability and support a free market economy. </p>\r\n \r\n<p>Revolution PAC donors are civically active, independent thinking, educated, and support conservative causes.   They want to end the status quo in Washington – NOW. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>These liberty-minded Americans are motivated to contribute to the following:   lower taxes, smaller government, elimination of Obamacare, gun owners\' rights, and protecting individual rights as outlined by the Constitution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the spirit of Ron Paul, Revolution PAC is building one of the strongest organizations dedicated to advancing the Liberty Movement.  Revolution PAC has recently launched a campaign to draft Judge Andrew Napolitano as the next Liberty Movement leader.</p>\r\n'),(63,'<p>Senior Conservative Donors is a file of individuals 65 years or older who have donated to a conservative cause or candidate in the last 12 months.   This file is update monthly, ensuring you are reaching the most recent and engaged conservative Republican donors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These donors will be responsive to solving our country’s economic crisis, repealing Obamacare, supporting our troops and veterans and continuing to elect men and women who will take a stand for legislation that supports conservative principles.   They will be especially responsive to the core issues that affect their age group such as Medicare and Social Security.</p>'),(78,'Megan,\r\n\r\nI have been trying to get in contact with you.  Can you please advise if you have copies of those documents I requested for the National Republican Victory Fund?  If you need a subpoena, please advise and I can obtain one.  Let me know either way.  Thanks again.  I can be reached at (703) 686-6257.'),(83,'Dear  Allegiancelistmarketing  Team,\r\n\r\n\r\nI thought you might like to know some of the reasons why you are not getting enough Organic search engine and Social Media traffic for your website.\r\n\r\nYour website is not ranking top in Google 